title: SPACIOUS FREMONT HOME 3 BED 1.5 BATH, EASY COMMUTE
posting_body: ['*$2750/mo rent; Available September 2022; Tenants pay Utilities*', '*3 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath, 1700 SF; 1st mo rent ($2750) and security deposit ($2500) due upon move in*', '-Apply at <URL>', 'This home offers spacious 3 bedroom, 1 Office, and 1.5 bathroom living.', 'Home has unique floorplan with original built ins and character you only get with older, historic homes.', 'Building is in good condition.', 'House is part of a duplex.', 'Vallantine Motorcycles will be on the Aurora side and the House is off the main road and thus noise is limited.', 'Tucked off of main road so you have a sense of privacy and quiet, but main road and restaurants and nightlife is just a block away.', 'House even has a partially fenced in side yard and grass area for pets and kids.', 'Unit has all the amenities and appliances except for a washer and dryer.', 'There is no washer and dryer in the home.', 'Tenants will have to go 1 block down the road to laundromat to do laundry.', 'Laundromat is very close and easily accessible.', 'Features-', '-Full, spacious, tiled kitchen', '-Large Great Room for Entertaining and spending time with family', '-Pergo/Wood floors', '-Fill Tiled main Bathroom with shower and tub', '-One (1) refrigerators', '-Plenty of storage and closet space', '-Large bedrooms', '-High ceilings', '-Full Bathroom', '-3 Bedrooms', '-Partially Furnished with some larger furniture pieces that are free and come with lease.', '-1 Office/Extra Bedroom', '-2 Off Street Parking Spots', 'Email or text Dustin at DPM for more information and to tour.', 'Thanks!']
